heading_context: Find people and technology on the Digital Marketplace
chunks.html_content:
All public sector organisations can use the Digital Marketplace to find people and technology for digital projects.

You can find:

  • cloud hosting, software and support, for example content delivery networks or accounting software
  • physical datacentre space for legacy systems
  • digital specialists, for example developers and content designers
  • digital outcomes, for example a booking system beta or an accessibility audit
  • user research participants and labs

heading_context: Find people and technology on the Digital Marketplace
chunks.html_content:
The buying process differs according to which agreement between government and supplier (framework) youre using.

Buying services through frameworks is faster and cheaper than entering into individual procurement contracts.

Find out how to:

  • buy through the Digital Marketplace
  • choose the right technology for your project
